author: Bianca Giulione
title: 2 Chainz Drops 2 New Tracks After Music Leak
text:
2 Chainz is back with 2 trackz. After his unreleased “It’s A Vibe” leaked Wednesday night, the Grammy award-winning rapper decided to properly share it along with “Smartphone.” “It’s a Vibe” could be described as “smooth af” and features a stellar trio: Ty Dolla $ign, Trey Songz and Jhené Aiko. “Smartphone” is incredible in its shade of Android phones alone.
Listen to both jams below.


2 Chainz, Gucci Mane and Mike Dean recently took over Jimmy Fallon’s Tonight Show with a performance of “Good Drank” with the ATL Trap Choir, which you can listen to below via Soundcloud. 2 Chainz is set to follow up on his last collaborative album with Lil Wayne, Collegrove , with Pretty Girls Like Trap Music , which will drop April 7. It will be his first solo endeavor since 2013’s B.O.A.T.S. II: Me Time and will likely feature music with Drake and Justin Bieber , which he hinted at earlier this year.

Revisit Migos’ “Deadz” from a couple weeks back featuring 2 Chainz right here.

In other music news, get the scoop here on what we know so far about Drake’s highly anticipated More Life playlist dropping soon.
